the fields with Calum and Jakob.


853
00:56:33.958 --> 00:56:36.552
She made it back to the
settlement and raised the alarm.


854
00:56:36.594 --> 00:56:38.729
We came back here
and...


855
00:56:39.230 --> 00:56:41.657
no Calum and no Jakob.

856
00:56:41.699 --> 00:56:43.058
Did the girl see
what attacked them?


857
00:56:43.100 --> 00:56:46.095
Well... she's in shock.

858
00:56:46.137 --> 00:56:47.796
What... what she says
makes no sense.


859
00:56:47.838 --> 00:56:49.506
What did she say?

860
00:56:49.840 --> 00:56:51.976
She said it was a dragon.

861
00:56:52.910 --> 00:56:55.237
She's in a bad way,
she... she's lost a lot of blood.


862
00:56:55.279 --> 00:56:56.881
She was bitten?

863
00:56:58.582 --> 00:57:00.175
Where is she?

864
00:57:00.217 --> 00:57:02.153
(squawking)

865
00:57:16.100 --> 00:57:17.568
She... she was just here.

866
00:57:18.069 --> 00:57:21.630
♪

867
00:57:21.672 --> 00:57:23.532
Everyone must leave.

868
00:57:23.574 --> 00:57:25.901
We can't protect them
in the field or in the village.


869
00:57:25.943 --> 00:57:27.736
It's no longer safe here.

870
00:57:27.778 --> 00:57:29.872
- And go where?
- Take them to the church,


871
00:57:29.914 --> 00:57:31.240
barricade the door shut.

872
00:57:31.282 --> 00:57:33.142
Food and water
can be fetched for,


873
00:57:33.184 --> 00:57:35.611
but under armed escort only.

874
00:57:35.653 --> 00:57:37.913
It is imperative
that we limit this exposure.


875
00:57:37.955 --> 00:57:39.223
Exposure?

876
00:57:40.057 --> 00:57:41.859
- Exposure to what?
- Seamus,


877
00:57:42.093 --> 00:57:44.628
you and your people
are being hunted.


878
00:57:45.796 --> 00:57:47.089
Water, I need water.

879
00:57:47.131 --> 00:57:49.258
(groaning)

880
00:57:49.300 --> 00:57:51.760
(screaming)

881
00:57:51.802 --> 00:57:54.863
(groaning)

882
00:57:54.905 --> 00:57:57.032
(screaming)

883
00:57:57.074 --> 00:58:03.272
♪

884
00:58:03.314 --> 00:58:05.774
(moaning)

885
00:58:05.816 --> 00:58:15.284
♪

886
00:58:15.326 --> 00:58:17.319
(screaming)

