00:59:20.691 --> 00:59:22.326
(match striking, gasps)

897
00:59:22.893 --> 00:59:24.386
Sorry.

898
00:59:24.428 --> 00:59:25.387
Oh.

899
00:59:25.429 --> 00:59:27.198
Can't sleep.

900
00:59:28.899 --> 00:59:30.826
Oh, me neither.

901
00:59:30.868 --> 00:59:31.802
Drink?

902
00:59:35.906 --> 00:59:36.974
Yes.

903
00:59:39.977 --> 00:59:42.046
(pouring)

904
00:59:48.986 --> 00:59:50.054
Who's Edith?

905
00:59:51.956 --> 00:59:53.257
My wife.

906
00:59:54.825 --> 00:59:56.694
Do you have children?

907
01:00:03.134 --> 01:00:05.069
Seems a long time ago now.

908
01:00:05.836 --> 01:00:07.872
Are they no longer
with you?


909
01:00:12.143 --> 01:00:14.311
We'd been stationed
to Gévaudan.


910
01:00:16.046 --> 01:00:19.150
They were plagued
by a wolf.


911
01:00:21.352 --> 01:00:24.346
Two people had been killed
in the first week,


912
01:00:24.388 --> 01:00:26.423
six the following.

913
01:00:27.725 --> 01:00:29.727
That's when the army
had been drafted in.


914
01:00:32.830 --> 01:00:36.233
There was talk
that the wolf was a curse,


915
01:00:37.301 --> 01:00:39.336
and if people need to know.

916
01:00:42.439 --> 01:00:44.742
The first time I saw it,

917
01:00:45.342 --> 01:00:47.912
it was covered
in fresh blood,


918
01:00:48.379 --> 01:00:50.381
just outside our village.

919
01:00:51.215 --> 01:00:54.919
By the time I got back there,
it was... too late.


920
01:00:56.220 --> 01:00:59.190
Thirteen people
had been killed by the beast.


921
01:01:00.324 --> 01:01:02.893
My wife and daughter
were among them.


922
01:01:10.535 --> 01:01:12.469
I'm so sorry.

923
01:01:25.482 --> 01:01:28.185
Did they ever catch
this wolf?


924
01:01:31.222 --> 01:01:33.348
Shortly after that,

925
01:01:33.390 --> 01:01:36.393
a band of traveling gypsies
came to Gévaudan.


926
01:01:37.394 --> 01:01:40.122
They said the curse
had had its revenge


927
01:01:40.164 --> 01:01:43.234
and was to be contained
in gypsy silver.


928
01:01:44.134 --> 01:01:45.528
They then traveled northwest,

929
01:01:45.570 --> 01:01:48.005
but the trail went cold
in Le Malzieu.


930
01:01:49.206 --> 01:01:52.309
Well, the gypsies had a claim
on my husband's land.


931
01:01:52.843 --> 01:01:54.436
My husband and the elders...

932
01:01:54.478 --> 01:01:55.379
That's enough!

933
01:02:01.553 --> 01:02:03.053
That's enough.

934
01:02:04.355 --> 01:02:06.056
I want no more talk
of curses.


935
01:02:06.991 --> 01:02:08.259
We've locked everybody
in a church,


936
01:02:08.459 --> 01:02:10.352
and I have nobody
working the fields.


937
01:02:10.394 --> 01:02:12.963
If you're here to help,
then please help.


938
01:02:14.566 --> 01:02:17.025
I just want this beast
or this wolf or whatever it is


939
01:02:17.067 --> 01:02:18.961
captured and killed.

940
01:02:19.003 --> 01:02:21.238
Tomorrow
I will set the traps.


941
01:02:35.986 --> 01:02:38.489
(carriage rattling)

942
01:02:41.559 --> 01:02:44.261
(squawking)

