963
01:05:07.772 --> 01:05:17.772
♪

964
01:05:22.085 --> 01:05:25.480
(whispering)

965
01:05:25.522 --> 01:05:27.683
(digging intensifies)

966
01:05:27.725 --> 01:05:32.254
♪

967
01:05:32.296 --> 01:05:34.222
(gasps)

968
01:05:34.264 --> 01:05:37.000
(breathing heavily)

