you can tell us?


1093
01:13:53.597 --> 01:13:55.099
Anything at all?

1094
01:13:59.804 --> 01:14:01.664
(drawer opening)

1095
01:14:01.706 --> 01:14:03.966
(paper rustling)

1096
01:14:04.008 --> 01:14:09.613
♪

1097
01:14:10.982 --> 01:14:13.842
"And Judas asked,
'What are you willing to give me


1098
01:14:13.884 --> 01:14:16.020
