1099
01:14:16.887 --> 01:14:19.949
So they counted out for him

1100
01:14:19.991 --> 01:14:22.492
♪

1101
01:14:23.327 --> 01:14:25.888
The silver from the dream.

1102
01:14:25.930 --> 01:14:29.058
You believe it was
the same silver given to Judas.


1103
01:14:29.100 --> 01:14:30.901
♪

1104
01:14:31.769 --> 01:14:33.738
Where is the silver?

1105
01:14:34.171 --> 01:14:37.066
♪

1106
01:14:37.108 --> 01:14:38.767
(knocking furiously)

1107
01:14:38.809 --> 01:14:40.978
McBride, open the door!

1108
01:14:41.712 --> 01:14:49.153
♪

1109
01:14:50.154 --> 01:14:52.490
We've all prayed
for your safety.


1110
01:14:52.923 --> 01:14:54.717
Some of the men
have joined Seamus


1111
01:14:54.759 --> 01:14:56.085
to go and hunt the beast.

1112
01:14:56.127 --> 01:14:57.619
We cannot control
what Seamus


1113
01:14:57.661 --> 01:14:58.496
is doing or has done.

1114
01:14:59.096 --> 01:15:01.098
I believe there is
a way to stop this.


1115
01:15:01.766 --> 01:15:02.733
Charlotte...

1116
01:15:03.367 --> 01:15:04.927
where is it?

1117
01:15:04.969 --> 01:15:10.165
♪

