01:15:27.792 --> 01:15:30.119
Saul,
send word to Molière.


1122
01:15:30.161 --> 01:15:32.588
The army must
be deployed immediately.


1123
01:15:32.630 --> 01:15:35.900
And, Saul,
I need a blacksmith.


1124
01:15:36.233 --> 01:15:37.760
